mapping.title: vocabularies - with suffix
mapping.description:
Maps vocabulary uri to the static directory on the web server.
Examples:
http://resource.geosciml.org/vocabulary/timescale/isc2013.ttl http://resource.geosciml.org/vocabulary/timescale/isc2013.rdf http://resource.geosciml.org/vocabulary/timescale/isc2013.html http://resource.geosciml.org/vocabulary/timescale/isc2013-opensearch.xml
mapping.creator: pidsvcadmin

mapping.title: vocabularies - no suffix
mapping.description:
Maps vocabulary uri to the static directory on the web server.
Examples: http://resource.geosciml.org/vocabulary/timescale/isc2013 http://resource.geosciml.org/vocabulary/timescale/
mapping.creator: pidsvcadmin

condition.description: ...of course it is a regular expression as documented https://www.seegrid.csiro.au/wiki/Siss/PIDServiceUserGuide#ContentType, and as such "+" is a special character there that needs to be escaped by preceding "\".
